description: Lists the capabilities associated with your Amazon Web Services account for your current or specified region. A trading capability contains the information required to transform incoming EDI documents into JSON or XML outputs.

nested_items.name: capabilities
nested_items.description: Returns one or more capabilities associated with this partnership.

nested_items.name: capabilityId
nested_items.description: Returns a system-assigned unique identifier for the capability.

nested_items.name: name
nested_items.description: The display name of the capability.

nested_items.name: type
nested_items.description: Returns the type of the capability. Currently, only edi is supported.

nested_items.name: createdAt
nested_items.description: Returns a timestamp for creation date and time of the capability.

nested_items.name: modifiedAt
nested_items.description: Returns a timestamp that identifies the most recent date and time that the capability was modified.

nested_items.name: nextToken
nested_items.description: When additional results are obtained from the command, a NextToken parameter is returned in the output. You can then pass the NextToken parameter in a subsequent command to continue listing additional resources.
